{"tid":2040513,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"點解想領養隻貓咁！撚！難！","createTime":"2020-05-28T15:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T10:01:56.000Z","uid":65116,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"eaa6459cebeb7a4bd547926cb346c80fc90b33a0","tid":2040513,"uid":65116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"上網睇咗好多間有得領養既機構大部份都好撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵到啲人自己搞既fb page又見佢好少貓可以比人領養<br />\n有無巴絲打咁岩有識人/自己有貓需搵緊人領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者有唔麻煩快靚正既渠道推介<br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申未養過但一定會盡奴才既責任 比滿滿既愛佢 錫到佢飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96af159dbfb329012cb0ab6b358e7d6fda76188c","tid":2040513,"uid":276676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比D耐性"},{"pid":"fc21998c8cd2f0f4e2357d83b6787aac4521ecaf","tid":2040513,"uid":65116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96af159dbfb329012cb0ab6b358e7d6fda76188c","tid":2040513,"uid":276676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比D耐性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:02:52.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2313cbf4a406fa694d081d978a3f2d0ec384b8","tid":2040513,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係上網見有主人要領養，<br />\n宜家準備緊窗網，之後就可以接主人返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b895794a1285f491289c43f93565b526671b6c8f","tid":2040513,"uid":184827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"re