tid":2040513,"uid":301551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T18:31:25.000Z","msg":"我有位朋友都係領養<br />\n但我唔知係佢好彩呀 定果間野d義工求其呀 定係間領養其實係賣貓 <br />\n佢果時好快領養到 仲要係第一次申請領養<br />\n一個月內由睇啱到申請到接到隻貓返屋企<br />\n申請完仲要好似幾日內就覆佢領養成功<br />\n講緊果時係佢屋企啱啱裝修完 都未執好哂d傢俬用品<br />\n係未執好到連大傢俬舖都未齊果款<br />\n貓義工就比佢接隻貓返屋企 我朋友果時好似仲要連貓屎盤都係求其買住個膠兜仔咁都比佢接<br />\n<br />\n我見到都唔係好相信佢咁順利<br />\n因為我聽好多係就唻問埋有意領養人祖宗三代做乜都領養唔到<br />\n但佢就好似填下表交d相就領養到咁"},{"pid":"7028d098da94f4ceb0aab10466c6c8cab90d08f2","tid":2040513,"uid":122915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"我都想養但連嗰啲私人義工都一定要家訪又盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b9835367cefabe0cbb21687661b1f41a7f5d1d","tid":2040513,"uid":65116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7028d098da94f4ceb0aab10466c6c8cab90d08f2","tid":2040513,"uid":122915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"我都想養但連嗰啲私人義工都一定要家訪又盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"我覺得家訪都OK<br />\n但有啲要埋咩住址證明 又要全家到齊 好憨鳩"},{"pid":"9fb7aac05d9e6470b4171152c14171b8810b8c33","tid":2040513,"uid":65116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3961ea7d87403460cbe0de58d6e39e7be54053ca","tid":2040513,"uid":63127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T18:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"唔熟荃灣 有啲難搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c776e35a8f7c342c94843226d2bbc1c699fc09b","tid":2040513,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T16:17:22.000Z","msg":"領養完先係惡夢既開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e66f705d35978f46c67e924d7987866a5a2cce3","tid":2040513,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"702